Narcos chronicles the life of legendary Colombian drug trafficker Pablo Escobar and how he established himself as the kingpin in the Colombian cocaine market. The show provides a fascinating account of life in the drug business. And, although we may argue that there are many similar plots, Narcos reveals the ugly truth behind the glamorised lifestyle. In fact, the show is based on the true story of Pablo Emilio Escobar Gaviria, who was said to be the richest criminal of all time. The second season of Narcos was released on September 2 on Netflix. Star Rating: 4/5